'''Cyborrean rabies''' was a disease that caused frothing of the mouth, and afflicted amphibicanoid [[Frog-dog/Legends|frog-dogs]].<ref name="Wolf">{{StoryCite|story=Lone Wolf: A Tale of Obi-Wan and Luke|book=SkyeWalkers: A Clone Wars Story}}</ref> [[Fi Skirata]] once joked that [[Darman Skirata]] caught it after he was bitten by [[Sull]]. [[Picaroon C. Boodle]] was accused of having it on [[Eriadu/Legends|Eriadu]], where he was quarantined and became a subject of [[Tuzin Gast]]'s [[Project Chubar]].<ref name="Dark">{{Wizards|url=default.asp?x=starwars/article/sw20050609a|series=The Dark Forces Saga|text=Part 5: Two Peas in a Pod}}</ref>

